keyFacts: Signed search warrant materials (affidavit and warrant) for case 20_MAG_6719n were transmitted via email on June 26, 2020.
The transmission was handled by an Assistant United States Attorney from the Southern District of New York.
The email originated from the address 'I St. Andrew's Plaza', which is associated with federal law enforcement in New York.
The document reference '20_MAG_6719n' indicates a federal magistrate judge case number, suggesting active investigative or legal proceedings.
